# usr/

User-facing documentation for Intent system, including installation guides, command references, and workflow tutorials. This directory contains three primary guides: a User Guide (task-oriented), a Reference Guide (comprehensive), and a Deployment Guide (installation and configuration).

## Files

- `user_guide.md` -- Task-oriented guide covering installation, getting started, steel threads, documentation, LLM collaboration, treeindex, AGENTS.md, Claude subagents, skills, upgrades, and troubleshooting
- `reference_guide.md` -- Comprehensive reference for commands, templates, directory structure, configuration options, best practices, and terminology
- `deployment_guide.md` -- Installation and configuration instructions for various environments, including global and project-specific installation methods
